name: Dishaa Pro
overview:
Dishaa Pro is a leading IT Training Organization based in the technology township of Noida, also home to many bustling IT Organizations. The training organization aims at guiding IT professionals with a working knowledge of ASP.Net with C# and SQL Server and honing their skills further on these programming platforms.

It trains enrollees in its state of the art facility where they get access to the latest in computing and software.
